	=cell C«%A»
	=cell enumeration value as an ASCII capital alpha
	=cell C«%a»
=row
	=cell C«%B» or C«%ব»
	=cell enumeration value in Bengali numerals I<(if supported)>
	=cell C«%b» I<(no effect)>
