	=cell block’s data
	=cell C«%d»
=row
	=cell C«%H» or C«%ह»
	=cell enumeration value in Hindu numerals I<(if supported)>
	=cell C«%h» I<(no effect)>
=row
	=cell C«%J» or C«%業»
	=cell enumeration value in Japanese numerals I<(if supported)>
	=cell C«%j» or C«%並»
=row
	=cell C«%N»
	=cell enumeration value as a cardinal number
